    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the iconic S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a high-pressure Double-VANOS variable valve timing system and individual throttle bodies, delivering a linear power band and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically flawless, the vehicle has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term structural integrity. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates, paired with the M-Variable differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its original factory kinematics with no bushing deflection or damper fatigue. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the paint depth is consistent across all panels with zero oxidation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
